BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:UpSurge Momentum: What Drives the Ecosystem Forward
DTSTART:20260519T213000Z
DTEND:20260519T203000
DTSTAMP:20260429T005254Z
UID:-1777423974.646279@codecollective
DESCRIPTION:Baltimore's innovation economy doesn't move in a straight line
 . Every year\, we see breakthroughs and bottlenecks\, big exits and persis
 tent gaps\, founders who landed the big win while others keep\n\nEvent Lin
